text: The Proclamation is an album by American jazz saxophonist Kamasi Washington. ==Track listing== Based on: #The Conception – 15:35 #The Bombshell's Waltz – 12:01 #Fair As Equal – 8:32 #Whacha Say – 4:56 #The Rhythm Changes – 8:34 #Lonely Woman – 11:19 #Like Someone In Love – 7:06 #Bobby Boom Dap – 10:50 Track 6 is a cover of Ornette Coleman, while track 7 is a cover of Jimmy Van Heusen and Johnny Burke. ==Personnel== Based on: *Acoustic bass – Miles Mosley *Drums – Ronald Bruner Jr., Tony Austin *Electric bass – Stephen Bruner *Keyboards – Brandon Coleman *Piano – Cameron Graves *Trombone – Ryan Porter *Vocals – Patrice Quinn ==References== ==External links== * *YouTube version of album Category:2007 albums Category:Kamasi Washington albums
title: The Proclamation
